#: ../../../release_details/9.6/multiscatter-ibl.md:1
msgid "Multiple Scattering Approximation for Image-Based Lighting"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.6/multiscatter-ibl.md:3
msgid ""
"VTK's PBR renderer now applies a multiple scattering energy-compensation "
"approximation when using image-based lighting (IBL). Previously, high-"
"roughness metallic surfaces appeared artificially dark because single-"
"scattering models lose energy at each bounce. The new approximation "
"redistributes that lost energy, keeping surfaces physically plausible across "
"the full roughness range."
msgstr ""

